nodes.text: The Campus COMPNOR Cadre was an Imperial-affiliated organization that was based at the Imperial Naval Academy. Titus Klev, who had served in both SAGroup and CompForce before entering the Academy benefited from his association with the Commission for the Preservation of the New Order as he was the type of wholesome Human that the propaganda branch liked to feature in media stories.
